      "instruction": "<p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, pat it dry with<strong> </strong>kitchen paper, then remove 2<strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>outer leaves </strong>per person and set these aside for serving</p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lettuce</strong> in half</p><p>Slice your<strong> tomato[es]</strong> finely</p>",
